what is javascript is and why we use it?
  examples
    Websites with javascript
      facebook
          -newsfeed
          -pop ups
          -client-side validations check fields before submitting
          (the code are running on the client side versus sending it
          in the the server to run code)
          -asychronous updates/saves
          -auto-fill; auto-search
          -show/hide part of a page
          -data visualization
          -games
          -test to see how users are using the site by mouse clicks and movements
    Where does this code run?
          -infinite scroll => when user scrolls
          -popups => user loads
          -code runs when in response to an action
          (event handlers will trigger the code)
  jQuery
    makes writing reused code easier
      jquery($) alias for jQuery
      jQuery is a library of codes to do things

      $("ul").append("<li>new</li>")

